text: Awon obinrin buruku wa fun awon okunrin buruku. Awon okunrin buruku si wa fun awon obinrin buruku. Awon obinrin rere wa fun awon okunrin rere. Awon okunrin rere si wa fun awon obinrin rere. Awon (eni rere) wonyi mowo-mose ninu (aidaa) ti won n so si won. Aforijin ati ese alapon-onle n be fun won
